{
  "page": "Lord Tully (father of Hoster)",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Tully\" title=\"House Tully\"><img alt=\"House Tully.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/6/61/House_Tully.svg/50px-House_Tully.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/6/61/House_Tully.svg/75px-House_Tully.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/6/61/House_Tully.svg/100px-House_Tully.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\">Lord Tully</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Tully\" title=\"House Tully\"><img alt=\"House Tully.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/6/61/House_Tully.svg/50px-House_Tully.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/6/61/House_Tully.svg/75px-House_Tully.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/6/61/House_Tully.svg/100px-House_Tully.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Titles</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_Riverrun\" title=\"Lord of Riverrun\">Lord of Riverrun</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Lord_Paramount_of_the_Trident\" title=\"Lord Paramount of the Trident\">Lord Paramount of the Trident</a></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Tully\" title=\"House Tully\">House Tully</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Rivermen\" title=\"Rivermen\">Rivermen</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Born</th><td>\nor before <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_228_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">228&#160;AC</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Calculation_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Calculation-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Died</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_264_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">264</a>–<a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_273_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">273&#160;AC</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Calculation_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Calculation-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Issue</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Hoster_Tully\" title=\"Hoster Tully\">Hoster Tully</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Brynden_Tully\" title=\"Brynden Tully\">Brynden Tully</a></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i> (mentioned)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i> (mentioned)</li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Lord Tully</b> was the Lord of <a href=\"/index.php/Riverrun\" title=\"Riverrun\">Riverrun</a> and the head of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Tully\" title=\"House Tully\">House Tully</a> during the early reign of King <a href=\"/index.php/Aerys_II_Targaryen\" title=\"Aerys II Targaryen\">Aerys II Targaryen</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Character\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Character</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Family\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Family</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Notes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Notes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Character\">Character</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lord_Tully_(father_of_Hoster)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Character\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>He was a follower of the <a href=\"/index.php/Faith_of_the_Seven\" title=\"Faith of the Seven\">Faith of the Seven</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot2.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot2.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lord_Tully_(father_of_Hoster)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>He became the head of his house after the death of the <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_Tully_(successor_of_Medgar)\" title=\"Lord Tully (successor of Medgar)\">successor of Medgar</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Succession_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Succession-3\">&#91;N 1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>When he passed away, he was sent down the <a href=\"/index.php/Red_Fork\" title=\"Red Fork\">Red Fork</a> in a boat following the <a href=\"/index.php/House_Tully\" title=\"House Tully\">Tully</a> funeral <a href=\"/index.php/Customs\" title=\"Customs\">customs</a>. The boat was set aflame by his eldest son, <a href=\"/index.php/Hoster_Tully\" title=\"Hoster Tully\">Hoster</a>, who fired a fire arrow. Hoster missed his first shot but his second arrow found the sail.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos35.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos35.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Family\">Family</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lord_Tully_(father_of_Hoster)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Family\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>His relation to his predecessor, the <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_Tully_(successor_of_Medgar)\" title=\"Lord Tully (successor of Medgar)\">successor of Medgar</a>,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Succession_3-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Succession-3\">&#91;N 1&#93;</a></sup> is unknown. One of the two was the father of <a href=\"/index.php/Celia_Tully\" title=\"Celia Tully\">Celia Tully</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Celia_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Celia-5\">&#91;N 2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div style=\"overflow:auto;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:separate;font: 90% sans-serif;\">\n<tbody><tr align=\"center\"><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td